    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Three new species of Kerria (Hemiptera: Sternorrhyncha: Coccoidea: Tachardiidae), a redesciption of K. yunnanensis Ou & Hong, and a revised key to species of Kerria" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215577> ;
